Entropic Touch					KEY:Chaos Knight ~ Entropic Touch				CATEGORY:Special Ability		TYPE:ClassFeatures.Paladin Class Feature.Chaos Knight Class Feature.Special Quality.Supernatural		SOURCEPAGE:p.18														DESC:A chaos knight can employ the forces of entropy with a touch to shatter a mind-affecting spell or effect currently affecting an ally. As a standard action, you can touch a creature to grant that creature a new saving throw against one mind-affecting effect, with a +%1 bonus on the save. If you target yourself, you can use this ability as a swift action. A chaos knight can use this ability %2 time(s) per day. This replaces lay on hands.|max(0,(CL=Paladin)/3)|((CL=Paladin)/2)+CHA
Blessings of the Maelstrom		KEY:Chaos Knight ~ Blessings of the Maelstrom	CATEGORY:Special Ability		TYPE:ClassFeatures.Paladin Class Feature.Chaos Knight Class Feature.Special Quality.Supernatural		SOURCEPAGE:p.18		DEFINE:ChaosKnightMaelstromHasFastHealing|0		DESC:A chaos knight can harness the unpredictable essence of the Maelstrom to bless a creature. When they use their entropic touch ability, a chaos knight can grant the touched creature a blessing from the table below that lasts for %1 round(s). Only one creature can have this blessing at a time. If another creature gains the blessing, the previous blessing ends. The creature rolls 1d4 and compares the result to the table below to determine the blessing. If the chaos knight targets themself with the blessing, they can roll twice and choose their preferred result. At 5th level and every 3 levels thereafter, the chaos knight can grant a blessing to one additional creature at a time (currently %2 additional creatures). This replaces mercy.|max(1,1+CHA)|max(1,(floor(((CL=Paladin)-2)/3)+1))	DESC:&nl; 1) The creature gets a +%1 sacred bonus to AC. &nl; 2) The creature gains a +%2 sacred bonus on weapon damage rolls. &nl; 3) The creature gains fast healing %3. &nl; 4) The creature gains a +%4 enhancement bonus to its movement speeds.|max(1,(CL=Paladin)/5)|CHA|2+(CL=Paladin)/3|min(40,5*((CL=Paladin)/2))		ABILITY:Internal|AUTOMATIC|Blessings of the Maelstrom 1	ABILITY:Internal|AUTOMATIC|Blessings of the Maelstrom 2	ABILITY:Internal|AUTOMATIC|Blessings of the Maelstrom 3	ABILITY:Internal|AUTOMATIC|Blessings of the Maelstrom 4		ABILITY:Special Ability|VIRTUAL|Fast Healing|PREVAREQ:ChaosKnightMaelstromHasFastHealing,1	BONUS:VAR|FastHealingRate|2+(CL=Paladin)/3|PREVAREQ:ChaosKnightMaelstromHasFastHealing,1
Aura of Chaos					KEY:Chaos Knight ~ Aura of Chaos				CATEGORY:Special Ability		TYPE:ClassFeatures.Paladin Class Feature.Chaos Knight Class Feature.Special Quality.Supernatural		SOURCEPAGE:p.18														DESC:A chaos knight treats their weapons as chaos-aligned for the purposes of bypassing damage reduction. In addition, the chaos knight treats attacks targeting enemies within 10 feet of them as chaos-aligned for the purpose of overcoming damage reduction. This replaces aura of faith.

